snippet.title: Amber Gott from LastPass, Free Mobile Use to Start, Two-Factor Authentication, Edge and Windows 10
snippet.description:
Amber Gott @lastpass, Marketing Manager for LastPass https://lastpass.com/ joins Mike Wieger http://wiegertech.com from Wieger Tech and the Open Mike Night Podcast http://omnpodcast.com  and Jim https://twitter.com/jcollison for show #226 of Home Gadget Geeks brought to you by the Average Guy Network, part of http://thegeeksnetwork.com community.

Please leave a REVIEW (iPhone or iPad) at https://itunes.apple.com/WebObjects/MZStore.woa/wa/viewContentsUserReviews?id=457300409&type=Podcast&ls=1&mt=1

Full show notes and video at http://theAverageGuy.tv/hgg227

Get the Interview ONLY with Amber at http://youtu.be/rANC4VbbPyE
